# bat (https://github.com/sharkdp/bat) — hestia defaults.
#
# The hestia theme is a custom .tmTheme linked into ~/.config/bat/themes/ and
# compiled into bat's binary cache by the dotfiles role (`bat cache --build`).
# Until that build has run, bat falls back to its built-in default theme.
--theme="hestia"
--style="numbers,changes"
--italic-text=always
